    note right of maybeActive
        setActive(true) makes the DropTarget accept drops (Active behavior).
        setActive(false) makes it ignore drop events (Inactive behavior).
        Value-sensitive: isActive parameter determines behavior mode.
        dragEnter, dragOver, dropActionChanged, dragExit, drop have no effect when inactive.
        addDropTargetListener throws TooManyListenersException if listener already registered.
    end note
